snippet.description:
Once upon a time, there was a happy giraffe who lived in a happy world, where the sun shone gently and the trees were always full of green leaves. But what she loved most in life was music. She spent her days swaying her long neck to the melodies of the wind, humming songs with the birds, and gently tapping the ground with her hooves to the rhythm of nature. In her world, everything was harmony, everything shone with joy, and happiness never ended. üé∂ü¶í‚ú®üòä

Thank you for listening and for always being there! üå±üåü
